' Congratulations on winning a Queen's Award in
=> @form_answer.award_type_short_name
=> "#{@form_answer.award_year.year}."
= "[#{@form_answer.urn}]"

= "Dear #{@name},"

' I am delighted to inform you that Her Majesty The Queen has been graciously pleased to approve the Prime Minister's recommendation that your organisation should receive a Queen's Award for Enterprise in
=> @form_answer.award_type_full_name
' this year. We have also informed your Head of Unit by email.

' Please read this email carefully as it contains important information about actions you need to do now.

' The Award will be conferred on
= @deadline.strftime("%A %d %B %Y")
' ,  (Her Majesty's birthday). Although you can make arrangements for publicity now, there is a strict embargo preventing public announcement or publication of any Awards information until
= @deadline.strftime("%H.%Mhrs on %d %B %Y")
' . You must not make any announcement about your Award, either to employees or outside your organisation, before this date.

' Under the terms of the embargo we will provide information to the media of the winners at noon on
= @media_deadline
' , and the list of winners will be published in the Supplement to the London Gazette on
= @deadline.strftime("%d %B %Y")

' Approve your Press Book entry

=> link_to "Log in here", dashboard_url
' to access the Winners' Dashboard to check the Press Book Notes (a factual account of why you have won the Award and not a promotional press opportunity), and your organisational details for accuracy, and let us know of any factual errors. You will also need to enter details of a contact for media enquiries, and click the "Confirm Press Book Notes" button by
= @book_notes_deadline
' . If you do not respond by the deadline we will use the proposed text together with the contact details that we already hold.

' A link to the Winners' Resources to gain access to the Queen's Awards emblems and Winners Manual is also on your online account.

' Two representatives from your winning organisation will be invited to attend HM The Queen's Reception at Buckingham Palace on
= @attendees_invite_date
' .  We will contact you closer to the time with instructions for submitting the details of the attendees.

' Congratulations once again on your Award.

' Yours sincerely

' The Secretary, Queen's Awards for Enterprise
